---
import ClerriLayout from '../../layouts/ClerriLayout.astro';
---
<ClerriLayout title="Conferences 2026" section="conferences">

<div class="page-head">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">14 · Events</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">Where the <em>buying audience</em> lives.</h1>
  <p class="page-sub">B2B dental search volume is structurally limited. Trade shows + industry publications are where DSO and group-practice buyers actually meet vendors.</p>
</div>

<div class="page-body">

  <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-progress-fill="conferences"></div></div>
  <p class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)">Progress: <span data-progress-here="conferences">0 / 0</span></p>

  <div style="overflow-x:auto">
    <table class="data-table">
      <thead><tr><th>Conference</th><th>2026 Dates</th><th>Location</th><th>Attendees</th><th>Clerri Priority</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><strong>Yankee Dental Congress</strong></td><td>Jan 29-31</td><td>Boston</td><td class="num-cell">~25K</td><td><span class="pill pill-grey">Regional flagship</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Chicago Midwinter</strong></td><td>Feb 19-21</td><td>Chicago McCormick</td><td class="num-cell">30K+</td><td><span class="pill pill-blue">Top-3 US show</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Hinman Dental Meeting</strong></td><td>Mar 12-14</td><td>Atlanta GWCC</td><td class="num-cell">10K+</td><td><span class="pill pill-blue">SE GP audience</span></td></tr>
        <tr style="background:var(--zest)"><td><strong>ADSO Summit</strong></td><td>Jun 15-17</td><td>Chicago</td><td class="num-cell">1-1.5K (C-suite)</td><td><span class="pill pill-rose">MUST SPONSOR</span></td></tr>
        <tr style="background:var(--zest)"><td><strong>DEO Operations Intensive</strong></td><td>Summer 2026</td><td>Dallas Renaissance</td><td class="num-cell">600+ owners</td><td><span class="pill pill-rose">MUST SPONSOR</span></td></tr>
        <tr style="background:var(--scrub)"><td><strong>ADA SmileCon</strong></td><td>Oct 8-10</td><td>Indianapolis</td><td class="num-cell">5-10K</td><td><span class="pill pill-wine">FINAL YEAR</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Greater NY Dental Meeting</strong></td><td>Nov 29 - Dec 1</td><td>Javits NYC</td><td class="num-cell">32K+</td><td><span class="pill pill-blue">Largest US dental</span></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="callout zest-hi">
    <div class="lbl">Strategic — ADA SmileCon ending after 2026</div>
    <p>The ADA confirmed it's <strong>sunsetting SmileCon after the 2026 event</strong>. Last chance for legacy-flagship sponsorship optics. Worth a top-tier booth + executive speaking slot for the "end of an era" press coverage.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Sponsorship decisions</h2>
  <div data-section="conferences">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="conf-01-adso" data-section="conferences" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">ADSO Summit June 2026 — secure sponsorship + Jim speaking slot</div><div class="task-meta">Highest DSO density of any event all year. Budget: $25-75K depending on tier.</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="conf-02-deo" data-section="conferences" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">DEO Operations Intensive — annual sponsor + speaking</div><div class="task-meta">Owner-CFO concentration. Budget: $15-40K.</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="conf-03-smilecon" data-section="conferences" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">ADA SmileCon (FINAL YEAR) — top-tier booth for legacy optics</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="conf-04-midwinter" data-section="conferences" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Chicago Midwinter — booth (30K attendees, top-3 US show)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="conf-05-gnydm" data-section="conferences" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">GNYDM (Greater NY) — assess booth or attend-only</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="conf-06-hinman" data-section="conferences" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Hinman (SE) — assess vs Yankee (NE) for regional priority</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="conf-07-yankee" data-section="conferences" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Yankee Dental Congress — assess vs Hinman</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <h2>Industry publications — must-be-in</h2>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card"><h4>Group Dentistry Now (GDN)</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">DSO C-suite focused. Highly engaged DSO/group audience. Sponsorship: newsletter, sponsored posts, podcast, conference partnerships. <strong>Co-promotes ADSO Summit</strong> — bundled buy worth exploring.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Becker's Dental + DSO Review</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Part of Becker's Healthcare network. DSO leaders + executives. E-Weekly newsletter, sponsored content, whitepapers, Becker's Dental Summits.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Dental Economics (Endeavor B2B)</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Practice owners, GPs, business of dentistry. Major print + digital — 100K+ practice owners.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>DEO (Dentist Entrepreneur Organization)</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Group practice owners ($1.2M-$100M+ revenue). Highest-value B2B audience density in dental.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="note-block">
    <div class="note-label">Conference + publication notes <span class="note-saved">✓ saved</span></div>
    <textarea data-note="conferences-notes" placeholder="Booth design decisions, sponsor tier pricing negotiations, leads from each event..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="topic-foot">
    <a href="/clerri/partners"><span class="dir">← Prev</span><span class="name">13 · Partners</span></a>
    <a href="/clerri/team"><span class="dir">Next →</span><span class="name">15 · Team & Operations</span></a>
  </div>

</div>
</ClerriLayout>
